data.description: Welcome to this charming and better than new home in the highly desired location of Liberty, Melissa TX. With 5Beds, 4 Full BA, and a loft, offers ample space for all your needs. Step inside and be greeted by the inviting interior featuring numerous upgrades. The open floor plan allows for seamless flow between the living areas, creating the perfect space for entertaining friends and family. Large windows flood the home with natural light, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere. The kitchen has everything you need. Retreat to the expansive primary bedroom suite, complete with a luxurious ensuite bath. The remaining rooms are generously sized and offer flexibility for a home office, gym, guest rooms. The loft area provides additional space for a playroom, media room, or study area. The expanded driveway provides ample parking space for you and your guests. Gather round the firepit to enjoy Texas evenings. Easy access to major highways, commuting to nearby cities is a breeze. Book now!
